Building Requirements
---------------------

 * Ant   1.6.5 and up (1.7 recommended)
 * Java  1.5 and up   (1.6 recommended)

Checking Out
------------

$ mkdir dtf
$ cd dtf
$ git clone git@github.com:rlgomes/dtf.git 

Building
--------

ant build

Run A Test
----------

cd build/dtf/dist
./ant.sh run_dtfx -Ddtf.xml.filename=tests/ut/arithmetic.xml